<div class="row justify-content-center mt-5">
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white">
                <h4 class="mb-0">Login to MCP Server</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <form action="/login" method="POST">
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label for="username" class="form-label">Username</label>
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="username" name="username" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label for="password" class="form-label">Password</label>
                        <input type="password" class="form-control" id="password" name="password" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="d-grid gap-2">
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Login</button>
                    </div>
                </form>
                <div class="mt-3 text-center">
                    <p class="text-muted">Default credentials: admin / admin</p>
                    <p class="small text-muted">For API access: api_user / api_password</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card mt-4">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5>Integration with Marketing AI Crew</h5>
                <p>This MCP server provides secure access to your n8n workflows, including integration with your Marketing AI Crew agents:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Strategy Agent</strong> - Updates targeting and competitor tracking</li>
                    <li><strong>Copywriting Agent</strong> - Sets up AI-generated ad copy workflow with approval</li>
                    <li><strong>Design Agent</strong> - Implements creative asset automation</li>
                    <li><strong>Campaign Manager</strong> - Builds Google Ads campaign creation automation</li>
                    <li><strong>Performance Analyst</strong> - Automates weekly reports and real-time monitoring</li>
                    <li><strong>Automation & Scaling Agent</strong> - Implements budget controls and autoscaling</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
